    public static enum Animal.HappinessLevel
extends java.lang.Enum<Animal.HappinessLevel>
    Denotes the happiness level of the animal. This is determined by the animal's health and hunger level. If all animals are happy at the end of the day the player will earn a bonus.
    See Also:
    Animal.happiness(), Animal.health, Animal.hunger, GameEnvironment.endDay()
